    • Constructor Detail

      • DriveTrain

        public DriveTrain()
        Creates an instance of the DriveTrain class.

        Configures motor controller current limits, durations.

        Slaves motor controllers to TalonSRXs.

        Initializes badlog.

        Enables drivetrain motor controller safety mode.

        Set drivetrain distance per pulse.
